reviews.text:
Decent cup of coffee

The place closes at 6:30.Revisited again but their last order on Saturday was 6:00pm. Couldn’t order avocado in toast 🥺

Open hours do not reflect actual order operation hours. Keep in mind and come early 😉

Who doesn't love Avocado? The Avocado Toast there is with a touch of lemon juice & mint, super yummy. Green salad as a side and the sour dough is nice too. I pair it with a Honduras hand drip. Perfect to start a day!
Decent food and good coffee. Tiramisu was a bonus. Spacious and cosy cafe located at the lobby of a hotel.

Had a great time here. Even if is in a hotel lobby there is a lot of space to seat and is quiet. I had an iced Americano and must say the coffee was flavorful not watery at all! Definitely a good spot to taste a good cuppa!!!
Fantastic coffee and the place is super comfy. Had a great afternoon, good vibes!

reviews.text:
Decent cup of coffee

The place closes at 6:30.Revisited again but their last order on Saturday was 6:00pm. Couldn’t order avocado in toast 🥺

Open hours do not reflect actual order operation hours. Keep in mind and come early 😉

Who doesn't love Avocado? The Avocado Toast there is with a touch of lemon juice & mint, super yummy. Green salad as a side and the sour dough is nice too. I pair it with a Honduras hand drip. Perfect to start a day!

Cafe好特別，乃位於柯士甸道與柯士甸路交界的新開酒店Page 148 的大堂內。
牛油果/芝士無花果/風乾火腿蘋果多士出色，香脆，配料豐富，價錢一律$78，算是合理。
double chocolate曲奇焗熱後，邊很爽脆，超正！
地方寬敞， 裝修別緻， 足夠的空間感，讓人在裡面一邊喝咖啡一邊看書或是工作，也是很不錯的選擇。連續兩天去試多士及咖啡。好味道！！
Decent food and good coffee. Tiramisu was a bonus. Spacious and cosy cafe located at the lobby of a hotel.

2019.01.28

Gesha Longberry, Guatemala @ Page Common

三選一，不知要哪一支豆。

"我們的豆都比較甜。"

真的嗎？隨意選了 Guatemala。

"這支豆像橙味的茶。" 咖啡師 Julia 遞上乾粉。

嗯，淡淡柑橘香。

Ideaology 在K11、亞士厘道和元朗也有分店。
"元朗店營業到二月就結束，去過嗎？。"
"沒有。"

一注水完成。

果味不俗，
但甜味沒有想像中豐富，
可能是期望過高吧，
Body 很輕很淡薄，
恰似咖啡師的溫柔。

後段微酸中帶茶感，
真的有像水果茶。

這是酒店大堂，
櫃檯一邊是 Coffee Bar，
另一邊是酒店前台，
二合一。
"住客 check in 可享 welcome drink。"
第一個想法是：那麼豆子會流轉得很快啊~ 好！
